Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.67,0:01:25.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我想我脑袋里有两种月亮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.54,0:01:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}虽然大部分人觉得只有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.61,0:01:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我和其他从没登过月的人一样看月亮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.75,0:01:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}要知道，我经常想这样会很有趣...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.79,0:01:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}不管它是否圆缺发出银光\N不管你有什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.79,0:01:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}每次\N我都在想有第二个月亮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.16,0:01:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}让我可以再次近距离接触它
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.43,0:01:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}是的，这确实比较难相信\N我曾经真的上去过
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.40,0:01:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我向你发誓，我是人类
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.97,0:02:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}这事情真的发生过
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.05,0:02:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我此生有3天把月球当作自己的家
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.65,0:02:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我来到这里是为了讲述
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.52,0:02:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}那是科幻小说.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.49,0:02:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我父亲出生的比怀特兄弟稍晚一些.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.74,0:02:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}他无法相信我可以去月球.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.74,0:02:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}但是我5岁的儿子汤姆.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.08,0:02:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}他却想这没什么大不了的.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.67,0:02:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}1968-1972年,\N有9艘美国宇宙飞船飞往月球
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.67,0:02:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}飞船上的宇航员们是唯一\N探访过异世界的人类
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.67,0:03:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}本片是透过他们的访谈\N来纪录他们登月的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.38,0:03:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}升空，我们升空了.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.14,0:03:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}飞离塔台
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.84,0:03:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}月影背后
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.44,0:04:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}1960年代初期\N苏联和美国为把人类送上太空进行太空竞赛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.31,0:04:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}有一天, 在试验发射中心,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.58,0:04:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}秘密工作的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.38,0:04:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}被叫到华盛顿去做简报.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.85,0:04:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}他们讨论在大力神火箭顶部
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.15,0:04:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}放个太空舱，再放个人,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.82,0:04:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}嗯...试着把他送到太空去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.80,0:04:36.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}当然，在那个时候,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.66,0:04:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}大力神火箭每隔一天就在卡纳维拉尔角发射一次
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.71,0:04:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}这好像是个非常，嗯，\N想短命的捷径
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.71,0:05:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}1961年4月12日\N苏联宇航员尤里加加林成为第一个绕地飞行的太空人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.45,0:05:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}不到一个月，阿兰谢帕德成为第一个进入太空的美国人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.41,0:05:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}他在太空飞行了15分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.61,0:05:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}20天后，1961年5月25日\N新当选的约翰F肯尼迪总统在国会发表演讲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.38,0:05:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}肯尼迪: 现在是美国大步迈进的时候了,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.61,0:06:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}展现伟大美国进取精神的时候了,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.18,0:06:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}是国家确立空间事务
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.52,0:06:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}领先地位的时候了.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.36,0:06:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}虽然在政治上, 这要击败俄国人,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.86,0:06:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}但是我们还怀着科学热情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.39,0:06:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}或者求知欲望,\N这要高于政治.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.40,0:06:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我相信我们的国家会让它
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.57,0:06:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}实现这个目标：\N在这个十年结束前
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.11,0:06:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}把人类送上月球\N并安全把他带回地球.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.94,0:06:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}这朴素中透着美丽.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.48,0:06:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}做什么？登月！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.48,0:06:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}什么时候？本十年末！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.25,0:06:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}他要我们挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.58,0:06:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}多数人认为不可能的事情，包括我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.15,0:06:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们进入太空是因为无论如何人类必须承诺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.63,0:06:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}自由的人必须完全共享一切
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.43,0:06:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}肯尼迪:\N但从真正意义上说,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.40,0:06:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}这不是要把一个人送上月球那么简单
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.77,0:06:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们可以肯定的说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.11,0:06:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}而是我们整个的国家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.54,0:07:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}为了全美国我们也要把人送上月球
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.27,0:07:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我做过一些现代飞机模型
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.24,0:07:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}大部分是小巧的木质装置
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.01,0:07:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}有一些真的可以飞，我很喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.71,0:07:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}所以我对真的飞机也很感兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.68,0:07:42.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}从我会记事时就是这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.56,0:07:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}当我小时候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.36,0:07:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我梦想飞行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.76,0:07:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}那是一战时一架飞机巡航
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.00,0:08:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}降落到我家的农场\N我爸爸帮它加油，然后我有幸坐了一次
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.38,0:08:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}绕我们的农田飞了一圈\N那是我第一次坐飞机
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.52,0:08:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}那时我4岁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.12,0:08:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}军队带着有翅膀的炸弹..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.42,0:08:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}把它们投向战场
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.52,0:08:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}这可能是电影\N也可能是真的新闻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.03,0:08:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}但我知道在什么时候，
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.23,0:08:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我想要的是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.63,0:08:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我知道我想驾驶飞机
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.54,0:08:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}1961年，我从试飞员学校毕业
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.11,0:08:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}然后在爱德华基地做战斗机试飞员的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.32,0:08:49.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}在试飞中心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.49,0:08:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}有世界上最“快”的学校
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.55,0:08:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}美国空军试飞学校
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.99,0:08:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}从这所学校
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.66,0:08:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}毕业的人便进入了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.96,0:09:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}航空学的尖端领域
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.58,0:09:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}试飞员的经验至关重要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.88,0:09:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}不仅要有军人的天分
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.69,0:09:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}还要面对大量的危险\N要有先驱精神
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.31,0:09:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}当你用超音速和在高海拔飞行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.15,0:09:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}学会如何生存并把飞机开回去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.69,0:10:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}是主要的任务\N飞的越高越快
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.46,0:10:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}危险越多，也越刺激
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.21,0:10:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我想我拥有世界上最好的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.67,0:10:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}无论从一开始飞行训练还是现在看电视都是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.11,0:10:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}一天阿尔谢菲尔德开火箭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.88,0:10:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}火箭表现的很完美！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.42,0:10:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}他比我飞的更高更快
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.55,0:10:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}重要的是，他造成了更多的轰动
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.12,0:10:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}他甚至上电视!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.03,0:10:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我怎么才能...\N得到那份工作？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.60,0:10:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}“我知道了一个秘密”！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.87,0:10:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}今夜带给你们..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.67,0:10:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}美梦成真！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.14,0:10:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}如同美味香甜可口
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.17,0:10:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}永不厌倦的甜点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.21,0:10:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}美梦成真！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.75,0:10:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}现在，如果你们悄悄把秘密告诉我，\N阿姆斯特朗夫妇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.08,0:10:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们会同时告诉观众们的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.02,0:11:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你们都悄悄跟我说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.09,0:11:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们的儿子今天成了宇航员
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.22,0:11:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}每个人都向宇航局的招聘递申请
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.53,0:11:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我想，这有几分公平
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.73,0:11:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}宇航局在63年早些时候招第三批宇航员的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.17,0:11:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我班上所有人都递交了申请
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.51,0:11:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}因为这是一个迎接新挑战的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.21,0:11:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}这当然听上去难度很大
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.35,0:11:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}因为人人都想成为其中的一份子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.59,0:11:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}这是为国争光t,\N我想成为其中一员.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.62,0:11:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}现在你什么感觉？阿姆斯特朗太太？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.89,0:11:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}如果失败...\N当然，没人知道；
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.83,0:11:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}但如果你的孩子是第一个登月的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.40,0:11:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你会什么感觉呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.70,0:11:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}呃，我想我会说上帝保佑他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.14,0:11:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}还要祝他走好运
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.98,0:12:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}一定会的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.72,0:12:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}在我合作过的太空人中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.76,0:12:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}那群太空人无疑是最棒的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.33,0:12:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}他们一点都不胆怯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.03,0:12:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}他们能力超群，刻苦工作
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.64,0:12:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}非常棒的一帮人.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.64,0:12:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}有一天，当你成为吉恩・塞尔南（阿波罗17号成员）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.48,0:12:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}年轻的海军飞行员，不管怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.38,0:12:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}明天，你就是美国的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.82,0:12:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}纵然你什么都没做
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.96,0:12:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}象汤姆沃尔夫写的《征空英雄:做你要做的》
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.46,0:12:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我想：啊！这听上去不错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.66,0:12:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}人们都会想做正事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.20,0:12:57.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我也一样，现在我也想，我要做正事！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.14,0:13:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}这份信念有几分不可动摇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.57,0:13:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}什么才是正确的?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.81,0:13:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}如果你是不朽的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.08,0:13:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你可以做任何事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.01,0:13:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}新太空人们潜心设计可供他们飞行的\N阿波罗宇宙飞船
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.93,0:13:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}没人真正知道怎么去月球
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.03,0:13:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}虽然书上有写道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.26,0:13:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}但是我们不知道怎么去做一些东西\N并且让它工作
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.67,0:13:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}这就是要把它们集合在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.44,0:13:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}让它们运行，然后修正不足
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.07,0:13:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}还有飞行员，太空人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.14,0:13:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}为什么，我们参与所有的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.41,0:13:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}和操作员工程师们一起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.18,0:13:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}一开始
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.05,0:13:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们把整个飞船
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.19,0:13:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}象切派一样分割开来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.12,0:13:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}把它分成10-15个不同的小块
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.93,0:13:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们给太空人一人一块
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.57,0:14:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}跟他们说：“这是你的\N我们要你吃掉它。”
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.71,0:14:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们要去月球
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.18,0:14:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}就在24万英里外
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.78,0:14:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}用一个300多英尺高的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.62,0:14:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}巨大火箭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.95,0:14:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}采用新金属材料
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.56,0:14:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}一些从没有过的新发明
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.73,0:14:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}精密的结合在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.66,0:14:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}比最好的表还要精密,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.67,0:14:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}这个前无古人的任务
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.17,0:14:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们要去未知的天体,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.74,0:14:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}并安全返回地球,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.01,0:14:43.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}他们会重新进入大气层
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.84,0:14:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}时速超过2.5万英里,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.38,0:14:50.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}产生的高温将是太阳温度的一半
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.02,0:14:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}几乎和这里一样“热”
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.25,0:14:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}要做这些工作\N要做这些工作
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.12,0:14:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}就要做的正确和迅速
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.79,0:15:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}要在本十年之前完成
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.93,0:15:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们必须要大胆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.90,0:15:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我回顾肯尼迪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.83,0:15:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}他是预言家吗\N他是梦想家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.27,0:15:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}他是精明的政治家吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.67,0:15:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}可能是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.34,0:15:15.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}他可能...三者皆是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.34,0:15:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们永远不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.88,0:15:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们也不知道当他倒下时(1963年遇刺)
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.72,0:15:32.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}给美国人民带来何等的挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.53,0:15:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}因此，我们行动时
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.30,0:15:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}求上帝保佑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.23,0:15:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们在这人类从未有过的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.64,0:15:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}最艰苦危险的伟大冒险上取得成功
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.48,0:15:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}1967年1月，美国宇航局为第一艘阿波罗飞船\N做了一系列模拟飞行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.06,0:16:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}一切都飞速流逝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.97,0:16:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}当时我被指派为第一次阿波罗任务的后备小组成员
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.87,0:16:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}事情有些繁乱\N也有很多问题
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.04,0:16:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}加斯格里斯姆尽了最大努力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.08,0:16:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}和他的小组成员艾德怀特和罗杰查非一起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.48,0:16:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}努力让飞船准备升空
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.65,0:16:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}在我们面对的巨大困难面前
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.36,0:16:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们有非凡的才智
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.20,0:16:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们深思熟虑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.03,0:16:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}尽可能规避风险
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.44,0:16:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}但是太空舱里的100%的氧气环境
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.54,0:16:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们真不想待在里边
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.12,0:17:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}还有 电线质量也非常差
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.65,0:17:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我问加斯，我说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.79,0:17:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}加斯，你怎么不在线路上发表下意见呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.52,0:17:12.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我说：太烂了，他们真应该好好做一下线路。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.46,0:17:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}真的很烂。\N然后他说：我不...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.96,0:17:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我不能发表意见，否则他们会炒了我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.67,0:17:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}他这样告诉我，真不敢相信
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.37,0:17:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}队员们现在地面上做测试
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.01,0:17:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}他们不打算升空
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.21,0:17:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我想我们，所有的宇航局的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.92,0:17:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}都不敢去想
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.55,0:17:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}如果在一个16psi（磅/平方英寸）完全氧气环境里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.99,0:17:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}有一点火花会是怎样？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.24,0:17:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我拿起电话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.21,0:18:01.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}他们问我：你是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.68,0:18:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我告诉他们我是阿兰宾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.94,0:18:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}他说：我们完了了。我们做试验...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.65,0:18:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}失去了队员
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.65,0:18:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}然后我问道...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.89,0:18:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}他们去哪了？你失去了他们？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.62,0:18:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我还以为他们要做试验了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.06,0:18:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}找不到队员了呢。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.83,0:18:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}不，他说\N我们失去他们了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.30,0:18:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我说：他们说不定在海滩小屋里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.80,0:18:32.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}他说：不是的。火灾。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.24,0:18:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我这才渐渐明白他们说的可能
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.58,0:18:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}和我理解的不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.81,0:18:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}现在我们中断节目给您带来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.98,0:18:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}特别报道.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.78,0:18:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}这位是ABC 科学栏目编辑\N朱尔斯 伯格曼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.89,0:18:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}太空总署官员今晚飞赴肯尼迪角
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.19,0:18:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}对今天早些时候因火花丧生的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.80,0:18:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我国首批阿波罗三人小组事故原因展开官方调查
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.10,0:19:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}他们在模拟发射最后时刻丧生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.61,0:19:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}无助的被困在太空舱内
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.16,0:19:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}事故发生在1月
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.96,0:19:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}1月27日
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.03,0:19:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们把他们安葬在阿灵顿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.67,0:19:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我还不知道我是否还要埋葬整个阿波罗计划
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.00,0:19:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}或者发生在我们三人....身上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.59,0:19:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}那是在60年代后期
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.79,0:19:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们正在和越南打仗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.09,0:20:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}还有许多种族问题
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.14,0:20:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我还不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.07,0:20:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}这个国家该何去何从
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.21,0:20:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们的整个文化在这个时期快速变化
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.55,0:20:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}公民权利变化
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.19,0:20:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}妇女权利变化
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.69,0:20:31.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}这些变化让社会朝向次级公开发展
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.93,0:20:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我想我们很明白越南的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.14,0:20:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}因为我们的很多朋友都飞去越南打仗去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.44,0:20:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}他们在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.41,0:20:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们却在太空计划
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.02,0:21:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我承认
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.72,0:21:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}对我的一些朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.09,0:21:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}有时候非常内疚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.30,0:21:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}那是我的战争
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.57,0:21:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}无论这战争是好的还是坏的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.61,0:21:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们不讨论好坏\N但那是我的战争，为国家而战
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.54,0:21:25.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我的兄弟们在生死存亡之间
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.98,0:21:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}甚至被俘虏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.52,0:21:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}而我的照片却经常上头版
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.69,0:21:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我经常在想他们是为了我而战
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.00,0:21:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}他们却有完全不同的看法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.87,0:21:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}他们说：无论做什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.64,0:21:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}国家的需求在任何时候至高无上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.11,0:21:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你们是计划的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.41,0:21:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们唯一要做的就是骄傲地昂首挺胸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.12,0:22:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}1968年，是这个国家
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.96,0:22:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}损失惨重的一年
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.96,0:22:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}有几起暗杀事件
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.77,0:22:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}不算好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.80,0:22:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}所以我们需要一个确定的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.17,0:22:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}让美国人有一种....成功的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.71,0:22:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}至少是满意的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.88,0:22:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}如果你是电影编剧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.75,0:22:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}没有比阿波罗8号更好的了！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.92,0:22:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}1968年11月，土星V型火箭准备\N第一次载人发射
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.33,0:22:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们从中央情报局听说
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.40,0:22:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}俄国人打算发射有人宇宙飞船
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.13,0:22:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}绕月飞行来羞辱我们
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.47,0:22:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}如果他们绕月飞行早于我们登陆月球
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.11,0:22:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}他们就赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.11,0:23:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们改变了阿波罗8号的计划
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.38,0:23:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}他们改变了绕地飞行计划
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.19,0:23:10.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}改成飞往月球
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.12,0:23:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}那是大胆的改动\N有一些冒险
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.39,0:23:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}但是是我们改变计划的时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.93,0:23:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}引擎准备
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.00,0:23:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}4，3，2，1，.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.54,0:23:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们升空了...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.67,0:23:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}阿波罗8号是第一艘离开地球进入外太空的飞船\N他们的任务是绕月飞行，而不是在月球着陆
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.77,0:23:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}阿波罗8号，这里是休斯顿
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.94,0:24:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你的轨道和导航器正常，完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.61,0:24:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}谢谢你，麦克
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.14,0:24:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}是的，你看上去很不错....
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.01,0:24:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}没有，只有当我们
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.31,0:24:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}真正第一次看到月球之前才能说不错
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.58,0:24:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们在陨石坑上方仅60英里
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.38,0:24:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你知道
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.65,0:24:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们就像3个学校里的孩子\N通过糖果店的窗子往里看
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.39,0:24:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们甚至忘记了飞行计划\N就在这里，离月球60英里
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.33,0:24:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}天啊,\N看看那张照片！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.57,0:24:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}喔，漂亮吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.70,0:24:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你拿到彩色胶卷了吗，吉姆？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.50,0:24:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}快给我照一张
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.44,0:24:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}抓拍张彩照
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.58,0:24:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}彩色外表
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.95,0:24:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们尽可能多照相
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.02,0:24:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}当然\N我们拍到了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.72,0:24:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}那张著名的地球升起的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.82,0:24:55.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我不得不让比尔安德斯拍照
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.66,0:24:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}因为他一直在要求！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.40,0:25:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}冷静，洛尔！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.37,0:25:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}好，我准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.57,0:25:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}噢，这拍的很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.57,0:25:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}当然，圣诞前夜
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.57,0:25:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}在圣诞前夜绕月飞行
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.38,0:25:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们想在这非常幸运时刻\N说点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.88,0:25:18.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们三个选择了\N读《旧约全书》
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.65,0:25:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们用耐火纸把书放在\N飞行手册后面带上太空
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.33,0:25:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}起初
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.06,0:25:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}神创造天地
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.80,0:25:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}地是空虚混沌
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.70,0:25:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}渊面黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.37,0:25:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}神的灵运行在水面上
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.58,0:25:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}神说，要有光
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.45,0:25:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}就有了光
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.76,0:26:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我想这是和月球非常棒的一次接触
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.83,0:26:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}在宇宙飞船上感觉很不错,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.73,0:26:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们在地球上打下的基础
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.60,0:26:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}让这一切得以发生.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.84,0:26:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我很喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.58,0:26:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}晚安 好运
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.85,0:26:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}圣诞快乐\N上帝保佑你们
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.18,0:26:28.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}平安回到地球
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.39,0:26:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}当我们回去
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.82,0:26:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}一位来自达拉斯，德克萨斯
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.03,0:26:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}无神论女士
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.70,0:26:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我不反对无神论
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.57,0:26:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}但她却控告我们
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.90,0:26:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}把教堂和国家\N混在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.31,0:26:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}她说那是不合适的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.01,0:26:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}可能吧，我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.67,0:27:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}再经过2次模拟飞行后,宇航局开始准备第一次登月
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.83,0:27:15.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}那时，我们开始练习着陆
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.14,0:27:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}阿波罗11号要着陆的地点,\N静海
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.61,0:27:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}引文我们有3个不同的小组在练习
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.14,0:27:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}阿波罗11号将于7月份升空
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.48,0:27:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}如果他们没成功\N2个月后我们就去
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.25,0:27:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}如果我们没成功
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.62,0:27:35.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}再过两个月\N就是阿波罗13号在11月去.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.22,0:27:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}所以在那年代结束前\N我们有3次机会
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.26,0:27:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}内尔，巴兹和麦克\N是阿波罗11号成员
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.80,0:27:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们知道他们是第一组
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.91,0:27:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}他们是非常棒的团队
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.14,0:27:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}他们进行的真的不错
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.74,0:27:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}麦克是很随和的人
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.08,0:27:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}他让事情变得轻易
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.45,0:28:03.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}如果让他得不到机会\N进入登陆舱登陆月球
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.65,0:28:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我会感到不安
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.39,0:28:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}所以这个念头闪过
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.06,0:28:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我便决定下来
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.59,0:28:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}有一个人不得不留在指令舱
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.53,0:28:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}另外两人去登月
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.96,0:28:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我有些遗憾..
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.80,0:28:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}作为指令舱指挥员\N所以...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.20,0:28:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我失去了在月球行走的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.07,0:28:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}不过话说回来\N我得到了机会
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.51,0:28:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}飞向月球
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.05,0:28:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}而且可能是第一个登陆月球的团队
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.49,0:28:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我知道巴兹
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.32,0:28:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}和我们比起来非常的聪明
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.69,0:28:47.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}他有个昵称\N“会合博士”
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.83,0:28:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}他喜欢谈论技术上的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.93,0:28:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}特别是轨道会合这方面
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.10,0:28:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}比如这条圆形轨道去这里
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.50,0:28:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}那条去那里
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.54,0:29:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}他在这方面做的很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.38,0:29:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}聚会时你不愿坐在他身边的
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.74,0:29:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}因为他老是讲会合的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.45,0:29:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}还不如在屋里
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.22,0:29:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}找个美女拉呱
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.72,0:29:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}他不管\N他只想讨论会合问题
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.36,0:29:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}一旦谈起来\N他能和你说一个星期
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.99,0:29:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}是的\N这就是我感兴趣的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.30,0:29:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我很敬佩内尔 阿姆斯特朗
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.60,0:29:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}他在我的同伴中是
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.14,0:29:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}压力下表现最冷静的
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.65,0:29:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}他就是“冷石头”先生
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.95,0:29:47.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}一个有趣的事是\N在内尔的训练中
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.82,0:29:51.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}有一个东西我们亲切的称为\N“飞床”
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.49,0:29:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}它很难看\N不过看上去设计精巧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.70,0:29:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}它效仿登月舱制作
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.37,0:30:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}内尔，他和我在都是邻居，有同一个秘书
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.04,0:30:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我记得一天早上
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.55,0:30:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我和他们几个回合，他们说
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.92,0:30:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你知道内尔今早从模拟舱里跳出来了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.43,0:30:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我说，不可能\N他说，真的
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.44,0:30:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}两三个人说：噢！
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.10,0:30:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我说：好吧我进去问问他
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.21,0:30:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我走进去，内尔..
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.34,0:30:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}内尔在那里\N什么事都没发生
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.18,0:30:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我说：办公室外面的人说
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.35,0:30:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你今天跳伞逃生了。。
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.28,0:30:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}他说：是。
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.58,0:30:49.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}他只说了"是"
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.62,0:30:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}这个家伙有好几次
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.05,0:30:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}死里逃生
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.66,0:30:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}但他从不说：我快死了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.63,0:31:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我快了， 你知道...\N我不知道...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.23,0:31:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}“嗯”仅此而已！
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.47,0:31:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我是说，他打算做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.63,0:31:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我想他可能去
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.07,0:31:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}大醉一场或者什么
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.87,0:31:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}但那不是内尔的风格，知道吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.14,0:31:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}他回去开始胡写乱画\N只能这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.04,0:31:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}要知道，太空计划还要继续！
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.58,0:31:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}1969年7月15日
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.17,0:31:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}明天，我们阿波罗11号宇航员...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.34,0:31:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}将代表美国
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.54,0:31:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}进行第一次尝试
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.05,0:31:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}把人类送上另外一个天体
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.39,0:32:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.60,0:32:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我是在发射三个星期前
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.70,0:32:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}戒烟的
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.70,0:32:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}那是我最美好的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.77,0:32:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}三天前\N好像还喝了点酒.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.78,0:33:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我不认为有人能真正睡着
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.52,0:33:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}发射那晚来临前\N你就在想
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.09,0:33:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}为了要做的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.33,0:33:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}肯定休息不好
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.41,0:33:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}这里是CBC新闻带来的阿波罗11号登月彩色报道\N登陆月球
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.18,0:33:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}阿波罗11号的伟大旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.95,0:33:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}由科洛格赞助
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.06,0:33:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}科洛格-每早给你多一点
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.89,0:33:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}这里是CBC阿波罗总部
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.36,0:33:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}位于肯尼迪航天中心\N记者沃尔特克伦凯特
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.13,0:33:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.43,0:33:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}发射倒计时1小时
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.50,0:33:54.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}29分53秒
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.04,0:33:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}只有1个半小时了\N一切顺利的话,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.07,0:34:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}阿波罗11号宇航员\N阿姆斯特朗，阿尔德林，柯林斯
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.81,0:34:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}将从39-a发射台升空
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.25,0:34:08.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}开始人类梦想中的旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.89,0:34:11.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}他们的下一站：月球
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.27,0:34:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}发射那天，有一些异样
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.71,0:34:33.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你从车里走向发射台时
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.08,0:34:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你...虽然已经习惯了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.45,0:34:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}坐车是美国方式
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.68,0:34:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}所以没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.29,0:34:46.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你到这个巨大的发射台
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.52,0:34:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}它很空旷\N没人在这里，很荒芜
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.43,0:34:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}只有一些工作人员,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.97,0:34:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}如一群蚂蚁忙碌
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.94,0:35:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你才不会感到孤独
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.34,0:35:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}然后突然之间没人了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.71,0:35:07.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你会想：上帝，你知道,\N可能他们知道我不知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.72,0:35:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们前往发射台时
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.45,0:35:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我有十分钟时间可以向外看
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.79,0:35:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}看太阳升起\N看波浪涌动
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.03,0:35:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}看到人们都在外面
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.90,0:35:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}就在想，这是真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.37,0:35:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}这些就是我要记住的
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.34,0:35:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}在他们出发前
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.51,0:35:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}他们的车子若隐若现\N安静地停在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.88,0:35:45.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我的后面是39-a台
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.52,0:35:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}是时候祝愿这三个人了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.15,0:35:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}承载着压力与希望
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.02,0:35:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}为了全人类的利益
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.60,0:36:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我感到\N全世界都在注视着我们
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.04,0:36:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}一旦我做错什么事情
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.04,0:36:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}因我而让其他宇航员做错什么
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.08,0:36:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}那么30亿人马上就会知道
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.42,0:36:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}这是一个非常不安的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.02,0:36:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}倒计时10分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.53,0:36:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们按计划整点过后32分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.53,0:36:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}升空
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.73,0:36:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}这里是肯尼迪发射控制中心
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.60,0:36:35.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我不知道为什么\N没有坐过火箭的人
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.73,0:36:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}不停问我\N“你害怕吗”
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.77,0:36:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}不，我们不害怕！
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.01,0:36:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}除非发生什么事情\N那是才会害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.44,0:36:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}倒计时还有不到2分钟了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.81,0:36:49.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}1分54秒
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.95,0:36:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}倒计时是非常负面的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.25,0:36:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你只希望不要出什么差错
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.95,0:36:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你会想：喔。这个过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.96,0:36:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}可还有下一个
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.36,0:37:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}当你很快就要发射时
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.49,0:37:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}突然间，好像有人打开了很大的电灯泡
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.40,0:37:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你看\N我想我们真的要升空了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.00,0:37:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我想这是真的\N我们要离开了！
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.87,0:37:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}30秒倒计时
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.07,0:37:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}宇航员报告感觉良好
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.01,0:37:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}25秒倒计时
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.61,0:37:24.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}20秒
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.82,0:37:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}15秒
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.62,0:37:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}内部导航启动
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.59,0:37:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}12, 11, 10, 9...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.49,0:37:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}次级火箭点火
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.23,0:37:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}6，5，4
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.46,0:37:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}3，2，1，0
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.08,0:37:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}升空的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.01,0:37:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}看着仪表上的读数变动
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.15,0:37:59.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}听着耳麦里的指示
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.25,0:38:04.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们升空了\N我们什么感觉？
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.22,0:38:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}一开始我们感觉,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.06,0:38:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们虽摆脱了地球引力,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.90,0:38:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}不过有些摇摆
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.47,0:38:17.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}可能导航系统问题
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.44,0:38:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}就好像是胆怯的新手
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.44,0:38:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}在小巷里开大车
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.28,0:38:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你要不断调整方向\N但又不是很自信
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.78,0:38:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}方向打来打去
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.41,0:38:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}下面这些巨大的发动机
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.72,0:38:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}好像“万向节”\N前后旋转
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.02,0:38:35.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}来保持平衡
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.22,0:38:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}好像一根铅笔笔直向上
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.96,0:38:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}还精确保持着平衡
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.83,0:38:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}随着发动机的震动\N坐在椅子上边气喘
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.67,0:38:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}边想：天，发射塔在那边仅几步远
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.24,0:38:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}那帮家伙可别把调整方向过头了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.94,0:38:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}当他们告诉你已离开发射塔
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.85,0:39:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你会高兴的说：呼，
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.48,0:39:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}太好了，不用担心\N撞上那个大家伙了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.62,0:39:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}可以自由飞行了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.04,0:41:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}金属可以抵抗这种震动吗
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.68,0:41:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}引擎了解这些晃动吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.48,0:41:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}因为摇晃和震动
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.79,0:41:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}比我想象的剧烈的多
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.62,0:41:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}他们把燃油歧管打开时
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.56,0:41:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们可以听到燃料进入管子的轰鸣声
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.80,0:41:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}这让我们知道\N从情感的角度来看
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.00,0:41:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们是要去月球的
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.57,0:41:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}这些声音和回响
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.37,0:41:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}来自那些引擎
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.51,0:41:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}5个已经点燃的引擎
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.31,0:41:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}它们让整个火箭晃动\N听着传来的声响
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.58,0:41:45.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}非常激动人心
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.55,0:41:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你并不孤独
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.99,0:41:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}许多人就在你的背后
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.25,0:41:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}等待这一切发生
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.66,0:41:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}因为每一秒钟
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.06,0:41:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}都非常有意义
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.20,0:42:04.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}飞行医生稍后告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.50,0:42:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}起飞时我的心跳144次/分
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.21,0:42:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}约翰是70
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.88,0:42:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我告诉约翰
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.88,0:42:18.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我老了，不能飞的很快
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.15,0:42:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我在想：我们为什么要做这些模拟飞行试验？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.02,0:42:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}因为如果在如此的震动下\N我要去按某个按钮
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.46,0:42:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我还真不能保证\N我能准确按到那个位置
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.76,0:42:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们上路了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.30,0:42:41.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}太棒了，太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.44,0:42:45.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我通过我的手掌\N就能控制飞船
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.24,0:42:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}如果导航失效\N或者偏离航线
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.96,0:42:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}飞到我们和地面不希望飞到的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.31,0:42:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我就打开开关\N控制超过
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.68,0:42:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}750万磅重的火箭
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.95,0:42:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}就用这只手
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.62,0:42:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}手动飞向月球
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.02,0:43:02.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我向你保证，我做了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.69,0:43:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}大量的训练\N我几乎...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.86,0:43:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我甚至敢自己飞
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.37,0:43:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我和她同呼吸共患难
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.04,0:43:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}它是那样特别
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.17,0:43:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}它给了我驾驭它的权利
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.07,0:43:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们被警告\N土星发动机关闭会
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.64,0:43:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}使加力
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.47,0:43:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}从4.5G到0
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.98,0:43:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}然后这个大火球
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.55,0:44:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}超长的助推火箭...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.15,0:44:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}就从你面前抛离
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.69,0:44:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}然后二级火箭点火
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.49,0:44:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}穿过火球
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.13,0:44:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}继续前进
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.69,0:44:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}收到，休斯顿\N可以分离了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.78,0:44:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}休斯顿，所有引擎分离完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.61,0:44:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你看上去不错
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.61,0:44:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}收到，讯号很好\N休斯顿
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.97,0:44:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}哈\N他们还是给我们窗户来看太空
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.51,0:45:04.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}进入地球轨道
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.51,0:45:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}绕地球一圈
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.35,0:45:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}然后就是紧张忙碌的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.35,0:45:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}因为要确定
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.22,0:45:14.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}在飞往月球前
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.72,0:45:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}一切工作正常
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.33,0:45:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}阿波罗11号，这里是休斯顿
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.53,0:45:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}准备TLI月球转移轨道射入，完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.97,0:45:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}阿波罗11号收到，谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.34,0:45:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}当你收到TLI的指令时
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.67,0:45:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你就要点燃引擎
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.04,0:45:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}把头朝向月球飞去
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.68,0:45:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}就这样！
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.56,0:45:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}点火
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.87,0:46:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}确认已经点火飞行
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.51,0:46:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.68,0:46:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}阿波罗11号，完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.91,0:46:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}每秒35000英尺
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.69,0:46:18.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}离开中.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.33,0:46:28.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}速度升至每秒35570英尺
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.83,0:46:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}高度，177海里
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.27,0:46:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}休斯顿，这里是阿波罗11号
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.97,0:46:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}土星发动机带来强劲动力
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.05,0:46:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}收到，11号\N我们已确认
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.28,0:46:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你们已经上路了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.59,0:47:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}在地球轨道上\N地平线是弯曲的
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.03,0:47:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}当你掉头前往月球\N很快
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.40,0:47:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你就得到回望地球的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.73,0:47:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}地平线慢慢变得更弯
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.77,0:47:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}一切突然间\N你感到
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.47,0:47:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}很奇怪\N但仍非常熟悉
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.74,0:47:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}因为你正在看地球的变动
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.04,0:47:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我透过窗口
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.15,0:47:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}看到这奇妙的景象
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.18,0:47:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}圆圆的地球
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.52,0:47:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}海洋是水晶蓝
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.86,0:48:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}陆地是褐色的
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.29,0:48:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}云彩和雪是纯净的白色
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.90,0:48:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}如同宝石一般
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.40,0:48:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们则挂在漆黑的太空
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.07,0:48:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}亲眼看到地球这种景象的人
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.68,0:48:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}只有去月球的24个人
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.58,0:48:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}当你看到那景象时，很奇妙
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.85,0:48:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}都不如这么大\N远远的在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.10,0:48:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}多么安谧宁静平和
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.50,0:48:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}又那么脆弱
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.87,0:48:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}有够怪异
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.57,0:48:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我看到地球这样我的最大感受就是
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.64,0:48:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}“天啊，这个小东西是多么脆弱啊”
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.95,0:49:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}看着地球慢慢后退
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.69,0:49:03.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}月球慢慢接近
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.72,0:49:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}这感觉绝对刺激
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.06,0:49:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}然后开始说：嗨，我们要去美丽的月球
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.60,0:49:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}拜拜，地球
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.48,0:49:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}信号到你那里的距离
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.68,0:49:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}大约是月地距离的一半
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.35,0:49:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们飞行了31小时20分钟了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.76,0:49:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们大约
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.62,0:49:40.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}还有不到40小时到月球
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.03,0:49:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们在路上
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.93,0:49:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}按计划飞行,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.46,0:49:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们脱去衣服，包好
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.37,0:49:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}吃饭，然后继续飞行任务
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.87,0:49:55.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}要知道，虽然很难吃
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.74,0:49:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}不过值得
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.15,0:50:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们在指挥舱有热水
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.11,0:50:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}然后拿点嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.82,0:50:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}剃须膏
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.85,0:50:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}带有卫生纸的刀片
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.36,0:50:11.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}这三四天里的剃须感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.42,0:50:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我难以描述有多棒
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.50,0:50:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}在我们的一览表里
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.90,0:50:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}有我的小孩和我妻子
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.94,0:50:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}的小小祝福
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.47,0:50:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}放在飞行计划本里
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.01,0:50:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}这是我的儿子查尔斯给我的
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.18,0:50:38.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}上面用画笔写道
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.28,0:50:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们爱你，来自查尔斯
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.62,0:50:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}另一面他画下了他想象中的
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.62,0:50:48.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}月球舱的样子.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.96,0:50:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}还有汤姆，那时快5岁了
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.20,0:50:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}他写道：亲爱的爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.87,0:51:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}平安回家。爱你的汤姆
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.22,0:51:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}这不是恐惧，这是担心
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.09,0:51:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}这两者之间是有区别的
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.96,0:51:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}这不是说你一直在害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.59,0:51:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}而是你一直有点担心\N至少我是
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.60,0:51:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}要知道，你不能确定一切都会工作正常
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.53,0:51:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}这些好像一条脆弱的链子
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.04,0:51:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你不希望链子上的任何一个链环断裂
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.94,0:51:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}一旦断裂，断掉的部分就没用了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.31,0:51:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}是的，你担心。\N因此你关注
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.18,0:51:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我经常想我是不是最胆小的一个宇航员.真的.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.62,0:51:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}当我从太空舱里向外观看
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.72,0:51:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我会想：如果这窗户爆裂
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.43,0:51:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我会马上挂掉
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.06,0:51:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}死亡就在一英尺之外
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.00,0:52:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}所有系统运行正常
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.77,0:52:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}开始转弯
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.87,0:52:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}在另一端再见
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.47,0:52:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}一切看上去不错
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.61,0:52:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}收到，完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.98,0:52:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们到达那里才真正看见月球
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.58,0:52:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}它看上去有些象科幻小说描述的
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.79,0:52:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}巨大的陨石\N慢慢移动
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.89,0:52:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}让你感到月球确实存在着
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.69,0:52:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}可你看不到
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.76,0:52:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们从一直是白天的情形
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.20,0:52:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}进入完全的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.10,0:52:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}就在去月球的路上
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.54,0:52:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}当我们进入黑暗时
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.14,0:52:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们就进入了月球的背影
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.82,0:53:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}当太阳光照射在
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.09,0:53:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}非常低的角度
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.16,0:53:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}会产生很长的影子
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.13,0:53:36.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}月球表面\N看上去非常荒凉
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.06,0:53:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}甚至有些可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.61,0:53:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我不认为月球
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.31,0:53:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}欢迎我们来到它的领域
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.41,0:53:56.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我感觉像是到了敌占区
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.32,0:53:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}一个...可怕的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.94,0:54:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}情势很紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.21,0:54:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}即使他们在模拟舱里训练过
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.88,0:54:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}也不能做到每次都成功着陆
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.89,0:54:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你垂直降落必须用\N合适的燃料
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.22,0:54:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}比如，用三分钟\N飞到一个合适的高度和速度
Dialogue: 0,0:54:38.59,0:54:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}没用....
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.90,0:54:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}有时候着陆雷达不工作
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.90,0:54:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们只好尽力去做好
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.57,0:54:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}尽量找个方法干好
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.54,0:54:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}这是个大任务
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.01,0:54:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}好，开始，总指挥
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.91,0:54:54.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}点火，好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.18,0:54:55.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}所有飞行控制已经打开
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.74,0:54:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}准备开始行动！
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.55,0:55:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}减速火箭？完毕！登月舱？完毕!导航？完毕！
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.98,0:55:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}控制系统?完毕!通讯系统?完毕!\N制导,导航和控制系统?完毕!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.72,0:55:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}电子系统？完毕！应急系统？完毕！
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.75,0:55:07.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}指令舱，着陆准备完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:55:08.66,0:55:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}阿波罗11号呼叫休斯顿
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.29,0:55:11.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们可以进行着陆了,完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.72,0:55:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}阿姆斯特朗:收到,"小鹰"已离巢
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.52,0:55:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}收到,看上去怎样?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.22,0:55:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}小鹰展开翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.54,0:55:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}Capcom就是太空舱通讯员
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.81,0:55:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}也是宇航员
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.21,0:55:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}也是唯一允许
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.81,0:55:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}和整个团队通信的人
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.08,0:55:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}告诉他去....完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.49,0:55:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我非常高兴A
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.42,0:55:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}能称为历史事件的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.69,0:55:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}如果我们获得成功
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.19,0:55:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}那将是极大的荣誉
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.39,0:55:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}柯林斯:看上去登月舱很好,小鹰\N不过上下颠倒了.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.99,0:55:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}阿姆斯特朗:人也是!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.19,0:56:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}小鹰,一分钟后着陆.你们小心
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.29,0:56:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}一会见!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.60,0:56:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}指令舱，我们继续进行航向指示
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.23,0:56:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你可以...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.97,0:56:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}可以继续减少动力输出
Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.77,0:56:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}继续减少动力输出
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.01,0:56:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}好了，伙计们，抓紧了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.41,0:56:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}看着着陆雷达
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.25,0:56:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们在着陆雷达指示的18000下行轨道处会合.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:41.02,0:56:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}收到
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.05,0:56:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}着陆雷达开始接受信号
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.06,0:56:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}作为“会合点”博士\N不管飞行手册里写什么
Dialogue: 0,0:56:52.13,0:56:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我还是要要雷达开启
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.77,0:57:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}如果我们放弃任务\N它还是会工作
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.57,0:57:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们也会迅速的重新
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.81,0:57:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}进行备用方案
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.44,0:57:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}休斯顿，我们有些数据丢失
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.91,0:57:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}不过看上去仍然不错
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.38,0:57:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}然后计算机警报
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.82,0:57:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}“计算机故障，1202”
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.82,0:57:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}什么是1202？
Dialogue: 0,0:57:17.35,0:57:18.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}阿姆斯特朗:程序警报!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:20.72,0:57:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}1202, 1202!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:24.70,0:57:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}所以, 当所有人都发警报的时候,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.80,0:57:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我的心真的沉下去了.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.27,0:57:32.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}"哦, 天啊, 我们遇到严重的电脑问题.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.57,0:57:34.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}1202警报.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.74,0:57:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}是的, 我们也遇到相同的问题了.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:40.74,0:57:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}1202号警报: 登月飞船的计算机数据传送过载
Dialogue: 0,0:57:46.79,0:57:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}登陆雷达正在传送数据,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:49.19,0:57:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}是电磁交会雷达,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.96,0:57:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}显然, 连结并没像麻省理工那些人预想的那样
Dialogue: 0,0:57:57.53,0:57:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}他们真是小心眼.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.83,0:58:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你在降落, 你需要雷达, 着陆雷达!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.30,0:58:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你在构造一个集合点, 你需要雷达...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.20,0:58:05.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}但你不要把两个混着用.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.24,0:58:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}但他们并不和我的想法一样.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:10.74,0:58:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}给我们解释一下1202警报的含义
Dialogue: 0,0:58:15.21,0:58:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}导航员, 史蒂夫贝尔斯, 回答...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:18.78,0:58:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们要继续飞行!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:20.92,0:58:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我听他跟飞行控制说
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.26,0:58:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我就说, 快点,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.79,0:58:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}"我们过去, 小鹰"
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.03,0:58:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们就过去了.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:29.90,0:58:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}小鹰, 这里是休斯顿, 继续着陆.完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:58:32.46,0:58:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}明白.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.77,0:58:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}继续着陆, 3000英尺.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.37,0:58:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}注意警报:1201.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.24,0:58:41.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}类型相同, 我们走, 接着飞.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:41.37,0:58:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}-好, 我们走.\N-我们走.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:42.81,0:58:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}相同类型, 我们走吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:44.38,0:58:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}47级.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:47.75,0:58:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}降落,燃料余2单位
Dialogue: 0,0:58:49.88,0:58:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}燃料告急. 他们不想说告急
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.95,0:58:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}然后尼尔l处境开始艰难了
Dialogue: 0,0:58:54.89,0:58:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}找到一个合适的降落地点非常困难
Dialogue: 0,0:58:59.73,0:59:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我也有些担心
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.70,0:59:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}因为他们的备用燃料并不充足.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.83,0:59:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们还是安静点吧, 麦克.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.10,0:59:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}400英尺, 降到9.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:08.84,0:59:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}好的, 现在只剩下燃料问题了.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:11.60,0:59:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}导航系统把他们带到了一个很大的巨石区
Dialogue: 0,0:59:15.31,0:59:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}这里不适合降落.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.51,0:59:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们的轨道拉平了
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.65,0:59:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}他开始低空飞行
Dialogue: 0,0:59:23.22,0:59:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}高速穿行在月球表面.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.15,0:59:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}糟糕的是你必须要减慢降落速度
Dialogue: 0,0:59:28.86,0:59:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}才能节省燃料
Dialogue: 0,0:59:31.59,0:59:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}因为你还需要燃料水平飞行,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.63,0:59:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}接着再次减速下降.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.30,0:59:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}这全都需要燃料, 明白吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:39.43,0:59:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}所以当他平飞的时候,我想希望他能成功
Dialogue: 0,0:59:43.54,0:59:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}要...要是有那些我们想避开的
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.51,0:59:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}漂石区和陨石坑
Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.57,0:59:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你就会有四种选择.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:51.48,0:59:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你可以短距离着陆,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:53.05,0:59:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}向左着陆, 向右着陆, 或者长距离着陆.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:56.22,0:59:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}短距离着陆, 你需要这样推起来
Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.15,1:00:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}但视野不好, 不清楚自己的位置.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:01.79,1:00:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}向左和向右也是一样.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:03.82,1:00:06.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}操作会很复杂.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:06.19,1:00:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}最简单的做法, 是只向前推一点
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.66,1:00:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}飞过去, 然后长距离着陆.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:11.33,1:00:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}有些石头和大众汽车差不多大小
Dialogue: 0,1:00:14.07,1:00:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你肯定不会希望一支脚落在石头顶上
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.14,1:00:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}另一支脚落在坑里.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:18.84,1:00:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}那样就太糟了.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:20.94,1:00:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}因此, 到了最后的关头 还是不清楚
Dialogue: 0,1:00:29.65,1:00:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们从指挥中心准备发出的, 有两个命令
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.42,1:00:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}第一个是"小鹰, 60秒",
Dialogue: 0,1:00:37.86,1:00:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}意思是他着陆可以多用60秒
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.86,1:00:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}在这60秒结束的时候,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:43.26,1:00:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}按照任务的规定, 我会发中止命令
Dialogue: 0,1:00:47.20,1:00:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我从没想过, 他到那时还没着陆
Dialogue: 0,1:00:49.94,1:00:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}因为, 我想只要引擎一停下
Dialogue: 0,1:00:51.97,1:00:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}他就会放弃
Dialogue: 0,1:00:53.77,1:00:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}他绝对不是想回到家 然后说,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:55.58,1:00:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}"燃料太少了, 我决定放弃了."
Dialogue: 0,1:00:58.98,1:01:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我认为没一个宇航员会那么做,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:00.78,1:01:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}那样是错误的!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:02.22,1:01:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}下降300英尺, 3.5 向前47
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.22,1:01:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}尼尔以为事情过去了
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.96,1:01:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}接着就按他的想法做
Dialogue: 0,1:01:09.99,1:01:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}通常来说是对的想法.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:12.99,1:01:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我认为没有人能达到
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.10,1:01:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}他那样高的水平
Dialogue: 0,1:01:19.10,1:01:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}75英尺, 只下降一半.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:23.14,1:01:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}60. 60秒.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.57,1:01:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}紧张的情绪弥漫在指挥中心
Dialogue: 0,1:01:28.51,1:01:31.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}就像是你可以感觉到一样.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:31.88,1:01:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你看不到, 但你完全可以感受到那种紧张.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:35.52,1:01:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}那真是...死一般的沉寂.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:45.66,1:01:47.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}下降三英尺, 2.5英尺
Dialogue: 0,1:01:47.39,1:01:49.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}激起了一些尘土
Dialogue: 0,1:01:49.63,1:01:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}下降三英尺, 2.5英尺
Dialogue: 0,1:01:55.40,1:01:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}向前拉, 向右一点点
Dialogue: 0,1:01:57.30,1:01:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}30秒!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:06.85,1:02:07.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}试着陆
Dialogue: 0,1:02:12.05,1:02:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}很好, 引擎关闭
Dialogue: 0,1:02:13.86,1:02:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}降落
Dialogue: 0,1:02:16.09,1:02:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}遥控装置, 全开
Dialogue: 0,1:02:17.29,1:02:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}减速火箭关闭
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.53,1:02:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}引擎关闭.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:21.33,1:02:24.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}413到达
Dialogue: 0,1:02:24.23,1:02:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们已经关闭.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:25.93,1:02:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}收到你降落, 小鹰
Dialogue: 0,1:02:27.94,1:02:30.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}好, 所有人, t-1, 准备执行t-1
Dialogue: 0,1:02:32.01,1:02:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}静海基地
Dialogue: 0,1:02:33.47,1:02:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}小鹰着陆啦!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:34.94,1:02:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}收到, 铛...静海,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:37.08,1:02:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们知道你们着陆了.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:38.35,1:02:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们有的人脸都吓绿了
Dialogue: 0,1:02:40.35,1:02:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们活下来了, 多谢.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:43.15,1:02:44.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}谢谢.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:44.42,1:02:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我太激动了,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:45.59,1:02:47.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我甚至说不出宁静号了
Dialogue: 0,1:02:47.69,1:02:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}说的好像是"拿-静号"
Dialogue: 0,1:03:02.94,1:03:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}专题报道!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:04.81,1:03:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你将会很高兴听到
Dialogue: 0,1:03:06.77,1:03:11.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}阿波罗11安全着陆了.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:17.42,1:03:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}变态小日本儿!!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:22.62,1:03:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我觉得, 对地球上生活的人来说,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:24.43,1:03:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}能活着来到月球上, 真是个奇迹.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:28.03,1:03:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}太了不起了!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:29.86,1:03:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}作为一个法国女人, 你怎么看?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:32.07,1:03:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}哦, 我想这真是个奇迹.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.27,1:03:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我相信美国, 我知道他们会成功的.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:37.77,1:03:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我想我们该出去喝一杯.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:40.04,1:03:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}但 我...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:42.21,1:03:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们真的很高兴, 那是...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:44.28,1:03:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}真的为我们所做的而高兴.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:45.68,1:03:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}那种成就感和自豪感, 真的很棒,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:49.35,1:03:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}为了肯尼迪总统和美国,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:52.92,1:03:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}说过的话, 我们做到了.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:05.73,1:04:07.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}哥伦比亚，我们成功了
Dialogue: 0,1:04:07.64,1:04:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}他着陆了 静海基地
Dialogue: 0,1:04:09.77,1:04:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}小鹰在静海，完毕
Dialogue: 0,1:04:13.01,1:04:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}是的, 我听见了整个过程!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:14.61,1:04:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}好, 干的漂亮
Dialogue: 0,1:04:17.01,1:04:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}太好了.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:23.65,1:04:24.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}后来我发现
Dialogue: 0,1:04:24.82,1:04:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我被描述成宇宙里
Dialogue: 0,1:04:29.79,1:04:34.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}最孤独的人, 这真能胡扯.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:34.43,1:04:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我是说, 我...还有指挥中心
Dialogue: 0,1:04:37.70,1:04:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}有一半的时间, 我耳朵都充满了废话.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:43.17,1:04:46.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}哥伦比亚, 休斯顿 情况怎么样?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:46.38,1:04:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}听着, 宝贝,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:48.04,1:04:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}所有的一切都很好, 很美
Dialogue: 0,1:04:51.71,1:04:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我很开心
Dialogue: 0,1:04:53.02,1:04:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我清楚当时的情况
Dialogue: 0,1:04:55.48,1:04:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}只有我一个人,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:57.85,1:05:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}当我独自在月球的另一端.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:01.06,1:05:03.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我还记得当时的想法,"天啊, 你看那边
Dialogue: 0,1:05:03.99,1:05:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}那里有30亿的人们,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:07.16,1:05:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}再加上月球上的两个,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:10.57,1:05:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}可是这里, 却只有一个...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:14.97,1:05:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}上帝才知道!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:16.47,1:05:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我...我知道那种强烈的感觉,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:19.18,1:05:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我觉得那不是孤独
Dialogue: 0,1:05:22.31,1:05:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我知道, 那也不是恐惧,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:24.25,1:05:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我清楚那种感觉,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:26.88,1:05:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}是一种很得意的感觉.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:28.95,1:05:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我很喜欢. 这种感觉太棒了.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:32.49,1:05:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}指令舱里一切顺利
Dialogue: 0,1:05:34.72,1:05:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}在我快乐的小家里, 我把所有灯都点亮
Dialogue: 0,1:05:38.23,1:05:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}一切都非常好. 那时我很享受.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:44.93,1:05:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}他们可能马上要打开登月舱门
Dialogue: 0,1:05:49.57,1:05:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}大约9点钟左右, 东半球的白天,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:51.77,1:05:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}从现在开始, 两小时以后多一点,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:54.51,1:05:57.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}39岁的尼尔 阿姆斯特朗, 俄亥俄州,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:57.55,1:05:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}瓦帕克那特市的居民,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:59.12,1:06:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}这次成功登月计划的指挥官
Dialogue: 0,1:06:01.68,1:06:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}将要从登月飞船里走出来,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:05.59,1:06:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}踏上月球的土地
Dialogue: 0,1:06:07.99,1:06:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}那会是怎样的时刻!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:09.76,1:06:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们正从电视上获取照片
Dialogue: 0,1:06:12.46,1:06:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}里面的对比度太大了
Dialogue: 0,1:06:15.03,1:06:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}当时, 我们的监视器颠倒了
Dialogue: 0,1:06:18.23,1:06:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}但我们也能得到正确细节的数据
Dialogue: 0,1:06:21.07,1:06:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我意识到, 所有的科幻小说家们
Dialogue: 0,1:06:23.77,1:06:25.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}那些写过去月球的人们,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:25.78,1:06:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我相信他们作梦也想不到
Dialogue: 0,1:06:28.61,1:06:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}全世界的人们正在电视里看到.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:35.22,1:06:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}尼尔, 这里是休斯顿,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:36.85,1:06:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}很清楚. 中断了, 中断了, 这里是休斯顿,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:39.79,1:06:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}啊, 无线电检查, 确认电视线路断路器.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:44.19,1:06:46.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}收到, 电视断路器
Dialogue: 0,1:06:54.94,1:06:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}好了, 尼尔,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:56.11,1:06:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们看到你从梯子上下来了.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:00.81,1:07:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}无论我去哪, 看到谁, 遇到谁,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:03.98,1:07:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}在那个时候, 甚至连孩子,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:07.75,1:07:10.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}都在看着尼尔在月球上迈出的第一步,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:10.62,1:07:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}全世界都在分享这一时刻.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:27.84,1:07:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}就绪了.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:39.32,1:07:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我就在梯子下面.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:42.25,1:07:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}飞船的梯子只能, 呃...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:46.82,1:07:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}延伸到距地面大约两三英寸,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:51.23,1:07:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}尽管表面看起来好像
Dialogue: 0,1:07:55.93,1:07:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}有一些纹理, 因为你离它很近
Dialogue: 0,1:07:59.54,1:08:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}那有点像是粉末.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:03.31,1:08:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}很有意思.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:12.65,1:08:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}好的, 我现在要离开飞船迈出第一步了
Dialogue: 0,1:08:24.16,1:08:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}这是一个人的一小步...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:29.43,1:08:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}却是人类历史上的一次飞跃.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:34.30,1:08:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}这是一个人的一小步...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:37.51,1:08:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}却是人类历史上的一次飞跃.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:00.23,1:09:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}尼尔似乎,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:01.87,1:09:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}比我想像的
Dialogue: 0,1:09:04.54,1:09:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}更有深度
Dialogue: 0,1:09:07.34,1:09:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我没有那么好的控制力
Dialogue: 0,1:09:11.44,1:09:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我可能已经...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:12.61,1:09:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}手舞足蹈了
Dialogue: 0,1:09:14.45,1:09:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}"呀吼" 知道吗?\N"伙计, 我在这!"
Dialogue: 0,1:09:16.78,1:09:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}那是...我觉得我会作出那种反应
Dialogue: 0,1:09:19.92,1:09:24.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}但他非常, 非常冷静
Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.19,1:09:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}然后说的话
Dialogue: 0,1:09:27.09,1:09:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}非常让人欣赏...太完美了
Dialogue: 0,1:09:32.00,1:09:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}从这看, 真美呀, 尼尔
Dialogue: 0,1:09:33.83,1:09:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}它有一种荒凉之美
Dialogue: 0,1:09:36.10,1:09:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}和美国的高原沙漠有点相似
Dialogue: 0,1:09:40.67,1:09:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}也不完全相同, 这里更美
Dialogue: 0,1:09:44.14,1:09:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}在我们的登月计划里
Dialogue: 0,1:09:46.75,1:09:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}要在梯子下面
Dialogue: 0,1:09:50.82,1:09:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}停留10-15秒
Dialogue: 0,1:09:52.52,1:09:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}检查一下着陆装置
Dialogue: 0,1:09:55.52,1:09:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}主要是看看我们的稳定性
Dialogue: 0,1:09:59.33,1:10:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}好的, 我们在高处
Dialogue: 0,1:10:01.06,1:10:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}很容易跳下去
Dialogue: 0,1:10:03.29,1:10:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}一步一步跳下去
Dialogue: 0,1:10:04.76,1:10:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}因此, 我决定
Dialogue: 0,1:10:06.63,1:10:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}接下来的时间要, 啊...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.44,1:10:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}要...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:12.81,1:10:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}注意一下身体器官
Dialogue: 0,1:10:14.61,1:10:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}少排了一点尿
Dialogue: 0,1:10:17.58,1:10:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}这样对接下来要做的
Dialogue: 0,1:10:21.95,1:10:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}会有一点帮助
Dialogue: 0,1:10:25.08,1:10:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}去吧
Dialogue: 0,1:10:26.79,1:10:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}这样, 每个人都有他们的第一次
Dialogue: 0,1:10:31.96,1:10:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}这样大家就公平了
Dialogue: 0,1:10:41.00,1:10:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我注意到他们唯一的变化
Dialogue: 0,1:10:43.07,1:10:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}在他们起飞之前
Dialogue: 0,1:10:46.54,1:10:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我记得是提前了一个月
Dialogue: 0,1:10:48.84,1:10:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}有人对他们说
Dialogue: 0,1:10:51.01,1:10:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}"你们要把美国的国旗插在月球上"
Dialogue: 0,1:10:53.78,1:10:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}所以我们把国旗拿出来, 插到地上
Dialogue: 0,1:10:58.78,1:11:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们真的没提前练习过
Dialogue: 0,1:11:19.81,1:11:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们在月球表面
Dialogue: 0,1:11:22.01,1:11:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我知道, 很多人在看着
Dialogue: 0,1:11:26.78,1:11:28.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}更多的人们在注视我们
Dialogue: 0,1:11:28.55,1:11:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}在历史上 没有两个人会受到这样的关注
Dialogue: 0,1:11:32.08,1:11:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们远离的, 不仅仅是距离的问题
Dialogue: 0,1:11:36.09,1:11:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}而是我们要带回去的事物中
Dialogue: 0,1:11:38.86,1:11:41.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}有些非常困难的事情要做
Dialogue: 0,1:11:41.36,1:11:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}离开这荒无人烟的地方
Dialogue: 0,1:11:43.76,1:11:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}然后再回去
Dialogue: 0,1:11:55.11,1:12:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}阿波罗11号之后, 一共有过六次登月计划
Dialogue: 0,1:12:00.11,1:12:05.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}有一次失败了
Dialogue: 0,1:12:11.36,1:12:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}谢谢, 13
Dialogue: 0,1:12:12.96,1:12:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你要是有机会, 我们想让你们多做件事
Dialogue: 0,1:12:15.76,1:12:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们想让你动一下液罐
Dialogue: 0,1:12:21.37,1:12:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}就绪
Dialogue: 0,1:12:25.67,1:12:27.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}当爆炸发生时, 当然了
Dialogue: 0,1:12:27.27,1:12:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我不清楚发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,1:12:29.71,1:12:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}休斯顿 我们有麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,1:12:32.88,1:12:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}13号，待命, 我们在解决
Dialogue: 0,1:12:38.08,1:12:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们看到氧气变成0
Dialogue: 0,1:12:41.39,1:12:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}然后又升到最高
Dialogue: 0,1:12:43.29,1:12:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}又再次降到0
Dialogue: 0,1:12:44.62,1:12:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}通过窗口我看到一些东西脱落
Dialogue: 0,1:12:48.62,1:12:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}一些东西脱落到太空
Dialogue: 0,1:12:53.90,1:12:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们有大麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,1:12:58.44,1:13:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我想, 当我看到氧气系统崩溃时,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:00.74,1:13:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我觉得我们要失去他们了, 真的
Dialogue: 0,1:13:03.14,1:13:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我以为回不来了
Dialogue: 0,1:13:06.31,1:13:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们尽量冷静下来
Dialogue: 0,1:13:08.55,1:13:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}尽可能的冷静下来
Dialogue: 0,1:13:11.75,1:13:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们要么呆在空中
Dialogue: 0,1:13:13.25,1:13:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}要么十分钟以后使用弹射装置
Dialogue: 0,1:13:15.96,1:13:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}回到我们出发的地方
Dialogue: 0,1:13:18.26,1:13:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}所以我们想到的第一件事就是:
Dialogue: 0,1:13:21.00,1:13:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}"我们要怎么做, 才能回去?"
Dialogue: 0,1:13:23.40,1:13:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}当然了, 我们还有登月飞船
Dialogue: 0,1:13:26.67,1:13:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}好象是, 丢弃飞船, 进救生舱
Dialogue: 0,1:13:30.10,1:13:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}在救生舱里回来
Dialogue: 0,1:13:34.91,1:13:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}飞船的动力还没完全消失
Dialogue: 0,1:13:36.78,1:13:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们还有十五分钟时间
Dialogue: 0,1:13:38.31,1:13:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}所以我们希望你们去登月舱
Dialogue: 0,1:13:41.55,1:13:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}再找到一些动力
Dialogue: 0,1:13:43.72,1:13:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你准备好你的程序了吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:45.79,1:13:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}好的
Dialogue: 0,1:13:47.01,1:13:52.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}在指挥中心, 其他的宇航员在想办法, 怎样控制损坏的飞船
Dialogue: 0,1:13:53.93,1:13:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我就尽力去学习, 怎样利用登月舱
Dialogue: 0,1:13:57.43,1:14:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}就像驾驶推进器,驾驶拖船那样
Dialogue: 0,1:14:02.00,1:14:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}在它们没有主要导航系统的时候
Dialogue: 0,1:14:05.91,1:14:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}怎样操纵杆,舵, 这些东西,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:10.01,1:14:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}约翰和我, 还有其他人
Dialogue: 0,1:14:11.61,1:14:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}在这次行动中, 一起努力让他们回来
Dialogue: 0,1:14:14.05,1:14:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}在一个叫作自由返航轨道上
Dialogue: 0,1:14:16.98,1:14:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}这样他们就可以回来了
Dialogue: 0,1:14:18.15,1:14:21.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}进入地球的大气层
Dialogue: 0,1:14:21.66,1:14:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}用合适的角度和速度
Dialogue: 0,1:14:25.49,1:14:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}阿波罗13, 2分钟以后点火
Dialogue: 0,1:14:29.46,1:14:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们利用地球的明暗分界线
Dialogue: 0,1:14:32.30,1:14:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}计算出我们的位置
Dialogue: 0,1:14:34.14,1:14:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们从飞船的窗子上目测地球
Dialogue: 0,1:14:38.21,1:14:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}确认点火
Dialogue: 0,1:14:40.21,1:14:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}引擎发动时,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:42.04,1:14:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}如果不能自动驾驶 凭我自己 无法控制地球始终在窗口内
Dialogue: 0,1:14:46.15,1:14:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}Fred-0保持飞船在地球的一侧
Dialogue: 0,1:14:48.52,1:14:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我来控制向上和向下...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:53.42,1:14:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我要把学习的功课再复习一遍
Dialogue: 0,1:14:55.72,1:14:57.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}可时间又很短
Dialogue: 0,1:14:57.39,1:14:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}但你会惊奇的发现, 你学得非常快
Dialogue: 0,1:15:01.26,1:15:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}休斯顿 你看起来不错
Dialogue: 0,1:15:03.20,1:15:05.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我的意识从"我们回不去了"
Dialogue: 0,1:15:05.80,1:15:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}转变成" 如果我们没搞糟, 他们就不会搞糟
Dialogue: 0,1:15:08.80,1:15:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们就没事了
Dialogue: 0,1:15:11.54,1:15:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们会回去的"
Dialogue: 0,1:15:22.25,1:15:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我深信, 这是国家航天局最伟大的时刻
Dialogue: 0,1:15:25.39,1:15:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}整个小队 都保持冷静和回应
Dialogue: 0,1:15:29.19,1:15:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}在一开始就做得很好
Dialogue: 0,1:15:31.26,1:15:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}这很重要 太棒了 他们太棒了
Dialogue: 0,1:15:34.93,1:15:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}登月, 和紧急情况的逃生
Dialogue: 0,1:15:39.00,1:15:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}这是两件完全不同的事
Dialogue: 0,1:15:43.37,1:15:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}一直到我平安的回到地球
Dialogue: 0,1:15:47.31,1:15:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我才感到非常的失望
Dialogue: 0,1:15:49.98,1:15:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}没能成功的登上月球
Dialogue: 0,1:15:52.98,1:15:59.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}但另外五艘阿波罗飞船则成功的登上了月球
Dialogue: 0,1:16:06.73,1:16:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}伙计, 当你站在这下面往上看
Dialogue: 0,1:16:08.00,1:16:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}那真是座大山,是吧?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:09.50,1:16:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们突然之间意识到
Dialogue: 0,1:16:10.97,1:16:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们正在山顶的下面
Dialogue: 0,1:16:13.20,1:16:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}太难以置信, 太漂亮了!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:15.60,1:16:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我向外看到地平线
Dialogue: 0,1:16:17.54,1:16:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我自己想,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:19.24,1:16:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}"天啊, 我希望彼得没降落在那, 因为我们要翻过去"
Dialogue: 0,1:16:22.94,1:16:24.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}进到阴影里了.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:24.41,1:16:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们把月球上的尘土吹得到处都是
Dialogue: 0,1:16:27.02,1:16:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}就像在雾中降落一样
Dialogue: 0,1:16:32.92,1:16:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}好, 我们到了!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:34.46,1:16:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}伙计, 我们到了! 看起来怎么样?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:36.93,1:16:38.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}如果说我整个飞行当中
Dialogue: 0,1:16:38.76,1:16:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}有一段时间是凝固的,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:41.50,1:16:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}那就是我们刚刚降落的前几秒
Dialogue: 0,1:16:45.17,1:16:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}一切都突然停止了.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:48.37,1:16:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们就在那里
Dialogue: 0,1:16:57.68,1:16:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}首先感觉到的就是,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:59.45,1:17:02.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}"哇, 这是, 呃...我在这做什么呢?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:02.25,1:17:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}这是个完全不同的世界!"
Dialogue: 0,1:17:04.49,1:17:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}啊, 这只是一部分...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:07.22,1:17:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}"无法表达的...你真的来到这了!"
Dialogue: 0,1:17:17.63,1:17:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}当你到达到月球, 停下来,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:20.14,1:17:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}走出去, 一个人也没有
Dialogue: 0,1:17:23.01,1:17:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}这个小登月飞船, 还有你们两个
Dialogue: 0,1:17:26.54,1:17:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}孤零零的站在这荒凉的地方
Dialogue: 0,1:17:29.08,1:17:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}这种感觉很不可思议, 非常奇怪...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:34.38,1:17:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}对两个人来说, 就是这样
Dialogue: 0,1:17:42.43,1:17:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}哦, 天啊. 太神奇了!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:47.13,1:17:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}太神奇了
Dialogue: 0,1:17:48.23,1:17:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}但是在太阳光里
Dialogue: 0,1:17:51.40,1:17:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}哦, 看那个
Dialogue: 0,1:17:53.17,1:17:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}是什么东西?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:55.24,1:17:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们在斜坡上边, 乔
Dialogue: 0,1:17:56.94,1:17:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们回头看那深沟
Dialogue: 0,1:17:58.64,1:18:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}真美, 真壮观
Dialogue: 0,1:18:11.62,1:18:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}爸爸, 真的是摇摆着前进, 对吧?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:16.49,1:18:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}以前从没像这样驾驶过.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:19.33,1:18:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}月球车非常好用
Dialogue: 0,1:18:22.47,1:18:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}很容易驾驶
Dialogue: 0,1:18:25.70,1:18:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}在这只有地球六分之一的引力下, 稍微一动
Dialogue: 0,1:18:28.74,1:18:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}就会离开地面一段距离
Dialogue: 0,1:18:35.31,1:18:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我开着月球车, 保持世界第一的下坡速度
Dialogue: 0,1:18:38.12,1:18:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我想时速大概有17km/h, 下坡
Dialogue: 0,1:18:44.69,1:18:48.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我甚至觉得, 试飞员瑟南
Dialogue: 0,1:18:48.29,1:18:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}都会感觉那速度有点快!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:50.36,1:18:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}这里有很多弹坑
Dialogue: 0,1:18:51.83,1:18:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}完全是运动型的驾驶
Dialogue: 0,1:18:53.46,1:18:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我要时刻盯着地面
Dialogue: 0,1:18:57.20,1:18:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}那里唯一不必担心的
Dialogue: 0,1:18:58.27,1:19:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}就是, 你不怕有人忽然从其它道上跑出来
Dialogue: 0,1:19:00.94,1:19:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}哦, 看这孩子爬山
Dialogue: 0,1:19:11.78,1:19:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我觉得那种感觉, 多数时候
Dialogue: 0,1:19:14.52,1:19:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}是一种敬畏
Dialogue: 0,1:19:16.85,1:19:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}月球是你想像不到的, 最美丽的沙漠
Dialogue: 0,1:19:22.49,1:19:25.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}未被开发, 无人涉足
Dialogue: 0,1:19:27.53,1:19:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}有一种震撼
Dialogue: 0,1:19:30.70,1:19:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}月球和黑色的天空
Dialogue: 0,1:19:32.84,1:19:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}形成鲜明的对比...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:35.81,1:19:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}令人印象非常深刻
Dialogue: 0,1:19:38.71,1:19:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}既兴奋, 又惊奇
Dialogue: 0,1:19:48.99,1:19:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们是真正的科学探索家们
Dialogue: 0,1:19:51.12,1:19:54.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们正在看的东西
Dialogue: 0,1:19:54.26,1:19:57.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}是人类从没想过的, 或者看到了
Dialogue: 0,1:19:57.39,1:19:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}却没从另一种角度考虑过
Dialogue: 0,1:19:59.46,1:20:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}用地球的角度去理解
Dialogue: 0,1:20:01.27,1:20:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}太阳系的角度 整个宇宙的角度
Dialogue: 0,1:20:07.81,1:20:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}那就是我们, 那就是我们所做的
Dialogue: 0,1:20:09.54,1:20:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们曾是科学探索者
Dialogue: 0,1:20:11.28,1:20:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}在那个时刻, 我们走出了飞船
Dialogue: 0,1:20:18.42,1:20:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}大卫. 我们搞点地质勘察吧
Dialogue: 0,1:20:21.72,1:20:24.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}先在这收集一点, 乔
Dialogue: 0,1:20:24.32,1:20:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}如果你去那里转转
Dialogue: 0,1:20:27.23,1:20:28.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}附近的边缘会有石头...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:29.09,1:20:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我想让你去捡起来, 作为土质样本
Dialogue: 0,1:20:32.90,1:20:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我说, 约翰, 看看脚印
Dialogue: 0,1:20:36.13,1:20:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你捡起来时, 看看它下面
Dialogue: 0,1:20:38.54,1:20:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}...有一厘米, 或者更下面, 是白色的!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:41.81,1:20:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}完全是白色的
Dialogue: 0,1:20:43.98,1:20:45.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}天, 你拿包了吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:45.84,1:20:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}准备好了
Dialogue: 0,1:20:48.08,1:20:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}好, 我们要取...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:49.65,1:20:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}阴影的材料...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:53.79,1:20:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}看, 这真美啊!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:33.59,1:21:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我-我从没有过这么棒的感觉...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:36.09,1:21:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}"哦, 我们做到了!"
Dialogue: 0,1:21:37.80,1:21:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我是说, 我们做了一部分, 但是, 呃...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:41.47,1:21:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我猜, 我担心的有点太多了
Dialogue: 0,1:21:45.40,1:21:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们从月球上拿走的东西
Dialogue: 0,1:21:47.71,1:21:50.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}比拿到月球上来的东西要多
Dialogue: 0,1:21:52.31,1:21:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}登月飞船只有一个发动机
Dialogue: 0,1:21:56.95,1:21:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}如果它出什么问题
Dialogue: 0,1:21:59.72,1:22:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你知道, 他们就全完了
Dialogue: 0,1:22:01.79,1:22:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}他们永远也走不了
Dialogue: 0,1:22:04.98,1:22:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}对于阿波罗11, 当时曾准备了一个演讲稿,\N以备他们无法安全离开月球时之用
Dialogue: 0,1:22:08.03,1:22:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}女士们先生们,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:09.23,1:22:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我是美国总统.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:12.63,1:22:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}早晨好, 美国的国民
Dialogue: 0,1:22:15.70,1:22:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}今晚, 我要告诉你们
Dialogue: 0,1:22:17.54,1:22:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}对所有美国人
Dialogue: 0,1:22:20.84,1:22:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}甚至是全世界的人们
Dialogue: 0,1:22:23.74,1:22:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}命中注定了
Dialogue: 0,1:22:24.94,1:22:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}那几个去月球探险的人们
Dialogue: 0,1:22:27.95,1:22:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}将在月球上安详的死去.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:31.45,1:22:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}这些勇敢的人们, 尼尔 阿姆斯特朗和埃德温阿尔德林
Dialogue: 0,1:22:35.19,1:22:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}知道他们自己无法生还,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:38.19,1:22:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}但他们也知道, 自己的牺牲, 会换来人类的希望
Dialogue: 0,1:22:44.76,1:22:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我的意思是, 这就是...
Dialogue: 0,1:22:46.37,1:22:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}一个公众人物所要说的话
Dialogue: 0,1:22:56.54,1:22:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}关舱门, 发动引擎, 上升, 继续
Dialogue: 0,1:23:06.32,1:23:11.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}很美, 以每秒26-36英尺的速度上升
Dialogue: 0,1:23:11.29,1:23:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}转向.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:13.73,1:23:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}慢一点
Dialogue: 0,1:23:16.96,1:23:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}平衡连接, 关闭
Dialogue: 0,1:23:19.30,1:23:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}非常稳定
Dialogue: 0,1:23:25.91,1:23:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}小鹰, 休斯顿要求人工返航开始
Dialogue: 0,1:23:31.58,1:23:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}高度2600英尺
Dialogue: 0,1:23:36.22,1:23:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}小鹰, 休斯顿, 1分钟. 你看起来不错
Dialogue: 0,1:23:41.45,1:23:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}哦, 天啊, 看... 太美了
Dialogue: 0,1:23:43.56,1:23:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}真的是很美, 你看飞船
Dialogue: 0,1:23:45.73,1:23:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}像一个金色的小虫, 周围是那些弹坑
Dialogue: 0,1:23:48.29,1:23:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}然后慢慢地变得越来越大
Dialogue: 0,1:23:51.76,1:23:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}它们就像是, 像是骑手
Dialogue: 0,1:23:55.30,1:23:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}那么精确
Dialogue: 0,1:23:58.37,1:24:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}然后就直升起来, 对我来说, 那是我的工作,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:04.58,1:24:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}和以前一样, 在两个飞船之间建立连接
Dialogue: 0,1:24:20.73,1:24:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}最后, 他们终于回到了飞船.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:23.86,1:24:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我抓住巴兹的两耳
Dialogue: 0,1:24:28.27,1:24:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我还要在他前额亲上一口,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:30.40,1:24:31.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我记得很清楚.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:31.87,1:24:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我把他带到这
Dialogue: 0,1:24:33.74,1:24:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}说, "那不是...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:36.88,1:24:39.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}太好的事情"
Dialogue: 0,1:24:39.25,1:24:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我也忘了, 好象拍了一下他后背
Dialogue: 0,1:24:42.08,1:24:43.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}或者是跟他握了一下手
Dialogue: 0,1:24:43.82,1:24:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你根本没时间坐在那回忆
Dialogue: 0,1:24:48.99,1:24:51.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}因为你已经完成了连接
Dialogue: 0,1:24:51.53,1:24:54.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}又过了一会儿...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:54.83,1:24:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你要准备好回去了
Dialogue: 0,1:25:08.94,1:25:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}最大的喜悦是, 就要回去了
Dialogue: 0,1:25:14.65,1:25:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}在驾驶舱内, 每两分钟,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:17.05,1:25:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}地球 月球, 太阳
Dialogue: 0,1:25:19.55,1:25:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}360度天空的全景就出现一次
Dialogue: 0,1:25:23.99,1:25:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}那种经历无法言喻
Dialogue: 0,1:25:29.76,1:25:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}突然间我意识到, 我体内的分子
Dialogue: 0,1:25:34.00,1:25:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}构成飞船的分子
Dialogue: 0,1:25:35.84,1:25:38.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}还有同伴体内的分子
Dialogue: 0,1:25:38.64,1:25:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}都是在这些远古时代的
Dialogue: 0,1:25:42.38,1:25:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}行星中进化而来的.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:49.08,1:25:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}在所有联系当中, 有着强烈的自我感.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:53.75,1:25:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}不是他们和我们, 而是," 那是我, 在一切当中
Dialogue: 0,1:25:57.73,1:26:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}是唯一的"
Dialogue: 0,1:26:00.33,1:26:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}那是一种非常迷人的感觉,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:03.16,1:26:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}那种感觉像是"哦,天啊. 哇, 是的" 一种感觉, 浮现出来
Dialogue: 0,1:26:31.26,1:26:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}阿波罗的返回非常关键
Dialogue: 0,1:26:34.23,1:26:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我最后一次看我的计算机
Dialogue: 0,1:26:37.40,1:26:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们以每秒39000英尺的加速度,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:42.97,1:26:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}换成公制是26000英里/小时
Dialogue: 0,1:26:47.91,1:26:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}来福枪子弹的速度也只有2000英里/小时
Dialogue: 0,1:26:53.72,1:26:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你在逐渐的加速
Dialogue: 0,1:26:55.92,1:26:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你的挡热板在升温, 在气化...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:59.42,1:27:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}它的碎片气化后, 被抛在后面,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:03.56,1:27:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}就像是在一个巨大的气泡里边
Dialogue: 0,1:27:13.97,1:27:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}在40万英尺时, 进入返航轨道
Dialogue: 0,1:27:17.01,1:27:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}那时你的速度达到了9万英尺
Dialogue: 0,1:27:19.17,1:27:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你是完全的直线下降, 自由落体
Dialogue: 0,1:27:28.02,1:27:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}最后的关键环节是...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:31.62,1:27:33.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}是, 哦...实际上,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:33.22,1:27:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我应该说有还两个环节,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:35.26,1:27:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}但是, 呃...最关键的是降落伞要打开
Dialogue: 0,1:27:42.23,1:27:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}主体出去了, 再次巨大的震动
Dialogue: 0,1:27:44.57,1:27:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}三个降落伞出来了
Dialogue: 0,1:27:55.04,1:27:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}三个橙白相间的都展开了
Dialogue: 0,1:28:10.03,1:28:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}都结束了
Dialogue: 0,1:28:11.19,1:28:12.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}这是最后一步...
Dialogue: 0,1:28:12.53,1:28:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}随后, 我们得出来
Dialogue: 0,1:28:17.03,1:28:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我还记得那美丽的海水.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:19.24,1:28:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们是从太平洋深处出来
Dialogue: 0,1:28:22.50,1:28:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}那是一种近乎于紫色的色彩
Dialogue: 0,1:28:26.08,1:28:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我记得我看着大海, 赞叹不已
Dialogue: 0,1:28:28.21,1:28:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}地球, 你有这么美丽的海洋
Dialogue: 0,1:28:39.86,1:28:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}对我来说, 最奇怪的
Dialogue: 0,1:28:41.76,1:28:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}是一切都像是时钟
Dialogue: 0,1:28:45.76,1:28:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我是说想魔术一样
Dialogue: 0,1:28:47.53,1:28:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}就在这个大时钟背后...
Dialogue: 0,1:28:52.20,1:28:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}似乎有一些魔法掺杂其中
Dialogue: 0,1:28:57.01,1:29:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}每件事都进行的那么顺利
Dialogue: 0,1:29:00.51,1:29:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}没有任何差错
Dialogue: 0,1:29:01.98,1:29:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我也没犯什么错
Dialogue: 0,1:29:21.20,1:29:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我知道 第一个登陆月球的人
Dialogue: 0,1:29:25.20,1:29:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}都肯定会被大家关注
Dialogue: 0,1:29:27.64,1:29:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}成为庞大公众所关心的人物
Dialogue: 0,1:29:32.14,1:29:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}这种关注, 会在执行任务时
Dialogue: 0,1:29:34.74,1:29:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}干扰到飞行员
Dialogue: 0,1:29:39.45,1:29:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}但任务结束了, 就无所谓了
Dialogue: 0,1:29:43.82,1:29:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}以后也是这样
Dialogue: 0,1:29:46.62,1:29:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你现在只是一个普通人,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:48.96,1:29:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}不仅仅是一个飞行员
Dialogue: 0,1:29:51.53,1:29:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}只是做了这个, 就更好了
Dialogue: 0,1:29:55.03,1:29:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}但是, "那家伙去过月球."
Dialogue: 0,1:29:57.40,1:30:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}现在, 无论我做什么, 后半生都会
Dialogue: 0,1:30:02.27,1:30:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}被很多人认出来
Dialogue: 0,1:30:09.88,1:30:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}真想不出尼尔 阿姆斯特朗有什么不对的地方
Dialogue: 0,1:30:13.12,1:30:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}这太神奇了, 他是第一个登上月球的人
Dialogue: 0,1:30:17.45,1:30:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}尽管现在看不到他了,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:19.56,1:30:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}更让人怀念他.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:22.43,1:30:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}真是个艰难的任务
Dialogue: 0,1:30:24.09,1:30:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我喜欢... 我热爱这么做
Dialogue: 0,1:30:26.26,1:30:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}但我讨厌失败
Dialogue: 0,1:30:28.43,1:30:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}艰难的任务
Dialogue: 0,1:30:30.00,1:30:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}是的...天!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:40.68,1:30:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}在阿波罗11飞行之后,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:42.68,1:30:45.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们三个作了一次环游世界的旅行
Dialogue: 0,1:30:46.55,1:30:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}无论我们到哪,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:48.92,1:30:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}所有人, 都不说"你们美国人成功了"
Dialogue: 0,1:30:52.29,1:30:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}每个地方, 他们都说"我们成功了,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:54.06,1:30:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们, 我们人类
Dialogue: 0,1:30:57.29,1:30:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们所有人, 成功了"
Dialogue: 0,1:30:58.90,1:31:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}还有, 我从没听过, 呃...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:03.20,1:31:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}不同国家的人们都有这个词" 我们, 我们..."
Dialogue: 0,1:31:07.51,1:31:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们总能听到
Dialogue: 0,1:31:11.54,1:31:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}欧洲, 亚洲, 非洲...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:15.65,1:31:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}不管去哪, 都是"我们终于成功了!"
Dialogue: 0,1:31:18.22,1:31:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}真是太有趣了.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:20.15,1:31:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}短暂, 却很奇妙
Dialogue: 0,1:31:36.26,1:31:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们再看一看月球\N这部片子里的人们, 是唯一从外太空看过地球的人
Dialogue: 0,1:31:53.58,1:31:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我感觉好像是站在一个高地上
Dialogue: 0,1:31:56.79,1:31:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}外太空的高地上
Dialogue: 0,1:31:58.09,1:32:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}科学技术使我到达那里
Dialogue: 0,1:32:02.83,1:32:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}但现在, 我看到的, 更重要的
Dialogue: 0,1:32:06.23,1:32:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}是那时我心里的真正感受
Dialogue: 0,1:32:09.73,1:32:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}科学技术却解答不出
Dialogue: 0,1:32:12.97,1:32:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}回答不了
Dialogue: 0,1:32:14.24,1:32:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}因为我在那, 你在...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:20.01,1:32:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你在地球上, 动态的, 非常庞大的
Dialogue: 0,1:32:24.08,1:32:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我感觉在世界上, 有太多的理想
Dialogue: 0,1:32:27.65,1:32:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}太多的逻辑性,却也总有些意外发生
Dialogue: 0,1:32:29.82,1:32:31.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}世界,也正因此而美丽
Dialogue: 0,1:32:31.56,1:32:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}控制的人, 不是你
Dialogue: 0,1:32:34.23,1:32:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}也不是我
Dialogue: 0,1:32:35.96,1:32:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我说的是精神上的感觉, 不是信仰上的
Dialogue: 0,1:32:39.66,1:32:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}那是这个宇宙的创造者
Dialogue: 0,1:32:42.40,1:32:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}凌驾于信仰之上的人
Dialogue: 0,1:32:44.57,1:32:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}不是我们自己创造出来, 来支配着我们生活的信仰
Dialogue: 0,1:32:53.81,1:32:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}一个网球俱乐部的朋友, 让我们去学习圣经
Dialogue: 0,1:33:00.02,1:33:05.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}在那个周末之后, 我对耶稣说, "我把生命交予你
Dialogue: 0,1:33:05.56,1:33:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}如果你真的存在, 来到我的生活里吧"
Dialogue: 0,1:33:08.36,1:33:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我相信他来了, 我有...
Dialogue: 0,1:33:12.26,1:33:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我有过这种安祥的感觉
Dialogue: 0,1:33:15.30,1:33:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}那是...很难描述出来.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:21.54,1:33:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}这有点戏剧性, 我们正在说我们的经历
Dialogue: 0,1:33:28.15,1:33:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我是说, 在月球上行走, 持续了三天
Dialogue: 0,1:33:30.85,1:33:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}这是伟大的经历
Dialogue: 0,1:33:32.85,1:33:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}但我跟着上帝前进, 却是永远的
Dialogue: 0,1:33:40.49,1:33:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我想, 如果你做一件事
Dialogue: 0,1:33:43.03,1:33:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}这件事非常特殊
Dialogue: 0,1:33:45.96,1:33:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}比如飞去月球, 再返回地球,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:49.13,1:33:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}每个人都告诉你, 这多么重要, 多么奇妙
Dialogue: 0,1:33:51.70,1:33:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}多么 多么 多么重要
Dialogue: 0,1:33:53.77,1:33:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}然后和其它事情比较起来
Dialogue: 0,1:33:57.24,1:34:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}原来很重要的, 就变得没那么重要了
Dialogue: 0,1:34:01.48,1:34:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我不是说我正视生活
Dialogue: 0,1:34:06.92,1:34:08.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}沉着冷静的面对
Dialogue: 0,1:34:08.89,1:34:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}只因为我去过月球, 但我试过.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:13.83,1:34:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}在去过月球之后,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:16.63,1:34:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}感觉有些关于陆地的争论,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:20.00,1:34:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}并没有以前那么重要了
Dialogue: 0,1:34:24.77,1:34:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们学习了很多关于月球的知识
Dialogue: 0,1:34:26.37,1:34:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}但我们真正要学习的, 还是地球
Dialogue: 0,1:34:30.88,1:34:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}事实是到月球的距离
Dialogue: 0,1:34:35.18,1:34:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你要竖起大拇指,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:36.82,1:34:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你还要把地球藏在你大拇指后面
Dialogue: 0,1:34:39.59,1:34:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你不知道的所有事...
Dialogue: 0,1:34:42.39,1:34:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你的爱人, 你的事业 地球本身的问题
Dialogue: 0,1:34:46.86,1:34:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}都藏在你拇指背后
Dialogue: 0,1:34:49.56,1:34:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们是谁根本无关紧要
Dialogue: 0,1:34:53.47,1:34:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}幸运的是我们有这个身体
Dialogue: 0,1:34:57.90,1:35:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}还在幸运的在这里生活
Dialogue: 0,1:35:01.97,1:35:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}和地球一起美好的生活
Dialogue: 0,1:35:11.45,1:35:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}这真的是个好地方
Dialogue: 0,1:35:13.39,1:35:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}可我们并没有照顾好它
Dialogue: 0,1:35:15.92,1:35:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我觉得应该引起足够的重视
Dialogue: 0,1:35:19.09,1:35:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}如果你愿意, 那真的会为拯救地球有所帮助
Dialogue: 0,1:35:27.57,1:35:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}从我们开始用双子星飞船以后, 地球已经又改变了很多
Dialogue: 0,1:35:30.14,1:35:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}有很多事, 比如城市污染
Dialogue: 0,1:35:32.94,1:35:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你在飞行轨道上都可以看见
Dialogue: 0,1:35:35.44,1:35:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}一座大城市
Dialogue: 0,1:35:37.18,1:35:41.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}被一种特有的气雾包围着
Dialogue: 0,1:35:41.58,1:35:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}真的是这样
Dialogue: 0,1:35:44.68,1:35:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们真应该为我们的子孙多想一想
Dialogue: 0,1:35:47.39,1:35:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}可我们在担心什么?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:49.46,1:35:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}汽油的价格
Dialogue: 0,1:35:52.32,1:35:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你看, 在美国, 担心他们每加仑3美元的汽油
Dialogue: 0,1:35:56.00,1:35:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我说, 太糟了, 你知道吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:00.50,1:36:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}从那时起,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:02.27,1:36:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我不再抱怨季节
Dialogue: 0,1:36:07.01,1:36:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我很庆幸, 还有季节之分
Dialogue: 0,1:36:09.01,1:36:11.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我不再抱怨交通阻塞
Dialogue: 0,1:36:11.18,1:36:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我很庆幸周围还有人
Dialogue: 0,1:36:12.88,1:36:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我回到家要做一件事
Dialogue: 0,1:36:15.02,1:36:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}去购物中心, 然后就只是呆在那
Dialogue: 0,1:36:18.89,1:36:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}吃着冰淇淋蛋卷, 看着人们来来往往
Dialogue: 0,1:36:22.46,1:36:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}然后想, "哦, 能在这真是太好了,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:25.56,1:36:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}为什么人们还对地球抱怨那么多?"
Dialogue: 0,1:36:28.56,1:36:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们生活在伊甸园里!
Dialogue: 0,1:36:34.57,1:36:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}想到从前, 如果用一个词的话,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:37.00,1:36:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我觉得应该是"幸运"
Dialogue: 0,1:36:38.51,1:36:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我真的感到十分幸运
Dialogue: 0,1:36:40.97,1:36:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你知道, 尼尔 阿姆斯特朗出生在1930年
Dialogue: 0,1:36:43.91,1:36:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}巴兹阿尔德林出生在1930年
Dialogue: 0,1:36:46.28,1:36:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}麦克柯林斯出生在1930年
Dialogue: 0,1:36:48.88,1:36:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你知道你有多幸运?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:50.95,1:36:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们刚好出生在一个恰当的时间
Dialogue: 0,1:36:54.92,1:36:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我觉得我的每一天都受到祝福.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:58.59,1:37:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}过去每一天, 我都会想, "太好了,
Dialogue: 0,1:37:03.20,1:37:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}美好的一天..."
Dialogue: 0,1:37:06.70,1:37:10.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}总会有人去, 却偶然的选中了我
Dialogue: 0,1:37:10.67,1:37:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}这真是太幸运了.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:40.64,1:37:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}有些小报上说
Dialogue: 0,1:37:43.17,1:37:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们其实是在亚利桑那州的一个峡谷里进行的
Dialogue: 0,1:37:47.01,1:37:48.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}可能那是一个很棒的想法
Dialogue: 0,1:37:49.01,1:37:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我不知道要怎么办
Dialogue: 0,1:37:50.75,1:37:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}抓住那个不信的人, 扯住他的衣领
Dialogue: 0,1:37:53.35,1:37:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}使劲晃, 来让他们相信
Dialogue: 0,1:37:55.15,1:37:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}历史上任何一件意义重大的事件
Dialogue: 0,1:37:57.25,1:38:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}人们总是会有这样那样的想法
Dialogue: 0,1:38:00.25,1:38:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我知道两个美国人想保守秘密很难
Dialogue: 0,1:38:04.16,1:38:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}因为肯定有一个会说出去!
Dialogue: 0,1:38:06.49,1:38:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你能想像几千人共同保守一个秘密?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:11.23,1:38:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们去过月球九次
Dialogue: 0,1:38:14.07,1:38:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我是说, 如果我们要编的话...
Dialogue: 0,1:38:18.31,1:38:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}为什么要编九次?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:19.77,1:38:23.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}真理不需要辩护
Dialogue: 0,1:38:23.85,1:38:26.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}没人, 没人...
Dialogue: 0,1:38:27.05,1:38:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}能把我们留在月球上的足迹抹去.


